Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然见到了「艾利尊战役」\N当时罗曼洛夫的部下罗博特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所见 基本不开口说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 他无法出任证人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之画…火的战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 多亏公安的通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此简单就能见面的理由就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他明天移送到你那之前 会把他在HESNER公司工作时的资料给你传过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象白费工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是从她没受到妨碍 平安无事这一点上能得出点结论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人有没有留下任何证据的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者罗曼洛夫体制并非如此团结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新人 马上就要下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:50.89,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,280)}{\fad(0,500)}战争之王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立的系统吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有逃亡之所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈仓老师已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向警察自首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察…不 GGP值得信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法信任他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥和父亲都憎恶GGP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把你交到那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同计划一样 我们将在和平纪念公园举行示威
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑Rideback到场的朋友请误随意骑行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看上去那么涣散
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的啦 Rideback被没收的人和被逮捕的人仅是少数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是为了阻止事态恶化才聚集的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力证明Rideback和琳姐的无罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力是好事 但BALON被没收了可得你赔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强 我们还是以安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从祥子姐那获得的琳姐的舞台照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}市内紧急事态示发布中\N一般车辆通行限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行书？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那通行证真的安全可靠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把后面打开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在磨蹭什么 快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是片冈南风 关系真到位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没是吧？到闹市里来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树藏于林 人藏于市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也想见见大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他们好象也要去参加对GGP的抗议游行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们约好了结束后碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子也要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然不参加 但菱田说之后会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始录了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳姐 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果琳姐出个万一 我都不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 祥子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前很担心 但看到录象之后就放下心中大石了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快些回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用邮件发的 没多大容量 有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能骑的很稳当了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次也想很琳姐并肩骑行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太长了 留点时间给…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计了可能成为BMA下一个\N袭击目标的国家机关以及车站等主要交通设施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经主干线警戒已经布置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但假设了其已经潜入都市内的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向警察发出了指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开「罗拉作战」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且在执政党议员片冈南风的关系网中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了反GGP人员活动的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可以根据反恐怖袭击治安维持法将其逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个罗曼洛夫大佐 南风是片冈龙之介的亲父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行适当的布置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队内部的系统完全是由独立的网络构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能从外部进行入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能破解敌方身份识别标示元系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的作战就是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有些发现吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈巴特科技公司搭建的独立传输协议网络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是无法侵入其系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却可能让其暂时停止运作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过伪造使用频率很低机器ID
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断向其网络输送阻塞其流量的BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个作战真正的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约好了的吗 什么都不问帮我干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在以往的交情上 就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个作战的确是伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真打算进攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗已经是动真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就如同你所说 很多人拥有其他的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是知道你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的背叛 我也不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在燃烧的ICBM基地中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓要向毁灭我的家伙复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不只是要单单杀掉那垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}我要将他从他拼命得到的地位上拉下 在绝望中将其扼杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么制作Fuego?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了尾形琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是舍弃了战场的男人的可悲的迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她却发觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驰骋于子弹与火焰的包围中的极限紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其中才能得以发火的自我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是一个18岁的普通少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她不应该获得的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 如果在那没发生恐怖袭击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没突破GGP的防御的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rideback已经让你身心疲倦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能像珠代前辈一样与Rideback平凡的渡日那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是国立第三剧院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的置身之所本应是那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我已经触手不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 放弃得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都想争个第一倒是和我一性格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却不喜欢轻易舍弃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在Fuego上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会勉强叫你再骑上Rideback的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是EW腕带可是作为部员的象征才给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是我的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会允许你擅自行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠代前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GGP从这个国家滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多人的话 警察也拿我们没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚 感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 冷静多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上场的时候你意外的能行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是国立第三剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琳姐原来所置身的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实比起骑车 更想看在舞台上跃动的琳姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我这样说出去的话 会被琳姐讨厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为因不能继续跳舞 最难受的是琳姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不知道舞台上的琳是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能如此那般驾御Fuego 我想是因为芭蕾的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来 驾御Fuego或许会对芭蕾起到一定帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳如果要返回芭蕾界的话 一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那家伙看上去干什么都能成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以放弃也许是因为琳没把自己的内心调整好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候出言相助才称的上朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子和小砚都是琳的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 如果还有所顾虑的话 可称不上真正的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙身为后辈 却毫不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要称我为琳姐的朋友 我的心理准备还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做朋友还需要什么心理准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们看来 你们已经是好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你难道是Rideback少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 我怎么比的上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她的FAN啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 秘之Rideback少女在这哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}刚才执政党最大派别领袖片冈南风议员被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}片冈南风议员被当作支援反GGP组织的嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}现在被扣押在疗养中的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 就算是跟接受过高度训练的骑手相比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这GRIMOIRE的战斗能力也毫不逊色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝佳的对手马上就会自己送上门来

Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警用Ride
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示威还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 抗议才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇起旗帜 共同努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个Rideback少女复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破了GGP防御的恐怖份子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她不是很危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样娇小的女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 搞的那么显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到会合的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}因恐怖袭击的车辆检查 本次电车将停站5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}给各位乘客造成不便 还请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急死人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能和大家见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 家父所在的医院 你不去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去帮手示威的监视行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片冈先生 部长叫您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有Rideback少女共生死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没有什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 雄起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rideback少女 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚 该回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 她完全听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 菱田 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警用Ride
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GGP的人也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知示威的人群中有骑着Rideback的通缉犯尾形琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥车通告各车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示威的人群中有通缉犯潜伏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其乘坐Rideback 有逃跑与抵抗的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以第4级警戒待机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他们有动作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙还真是狗仗人势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GGP滚出这个国家去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让你们肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去 滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是该跑啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}检查结束 本车将要发车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不辛呢 亲人被当作是嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经调查过罗曼洛夫大佐的经历了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GGP整个组织正在老龄化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热衷于战争的旧体制就是以他为代表的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想表达什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您父亲的事情由我们来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 有事需要您动尊身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭发HESNER公司 只能依靠您的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想威胁我屈服于你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新次序的建立需要好故事来铺垫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上舞台的人需要分配其职务与给予其报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在布置车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菱田 快想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我想也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚 快下车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菱田前辈 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去公园外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号车 目标通过公路逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以违反道路交通法将其逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琳姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且珠代前辈也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小砚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号车追着他 2号车饶到前面截他进路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被追？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的通路被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳姐 那个…请再次登上舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看琳姐在舞台上的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚 在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看着我 琳姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在时 我特训的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也飞给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚被… 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的…这不是真的…这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我知道了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小砚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 如果不是你制造出这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚她…小砚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小砚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与你的迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的迷恋将小砚害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:22:00.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}彼が笑っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:08.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}気付いたら　あなたを思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:15.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}彼と繋ぐ手も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:23.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}感じてる　あなたの温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:28.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}思い出を切り取って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}胸から追い出したって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}記憶を蹴飛ばしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:40.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いまだに　あなたを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今　時が過ぎ去り　季節を巡り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:49.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あの笑顔　白く霞んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心はそう　あなたを忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:57.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}もう二度と会えなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑いあう写真簿を倒しても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:06.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}溢れ出す思いを隠しても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:09.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心は忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:14.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あなたとの記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:22:00.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看着他的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:08.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}恍然间 却又忆起你的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:15.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与他相依牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:23.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}仍还是 你的温度残留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:28.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纵然能切断回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纵然能心无旁念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纵然能忘却记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:40.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}却依然对你怀有留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}时光飞逝 四季轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:49.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你的笑容早已模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心中还是对你难以忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:57.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再也无法相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:01.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使合上相视而笑的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:06.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使苦苦压抑喷涌的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:09.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}仍难忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:14.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与你相伴的记忆


